## ADVANCED TOPICS FOR EXPERIENCED TRADERS

### CORRELATION TRADING
**Concept**: Multiple forex pairs move together (EUR/USD, GBP/USD, EUR/GBP)
**Advantage**: Can hedge or confirm setups across correlated pairs
**Tool**: Correlation coefficient calculator (checking which pairs move together)

### MULTI-ASSET STRATEGIES
**Example**: Long S&P 500 + Long EUR/USD = capturing both stock + forex momentum
**Risk**: Over-exposure if both move against you
**Management**: Count both as positions when calculating exposure

### NEWS SENTIMENT TRADING
**Concept**: Trade currency/index that has positive news while avoiding negative news
**Tools**: News sentiment indicators, trade headlines real-time
**Risk**: Extreme volatility, gaps, slippage

### SWING TRADING INDICES
**Longer timeframe = Weekly/daily charts**
**Benefit**: Can hold 1-4 weeks, less day-to-day stress
**Positions**: 2-3 at a time across different indices
**Advantage**: Fundamental analysis works better on longer timeframes

