**Most traders fail.** Statistics show 90% lose money within 6 months.

**Why?**
- Lack of discipline (chasing trades, revenge trading)
- No proper risk management (risking too much per trade)
- Insufficient backtesting (jumping to live trading too fast)
- Overestimating skill (thinking they can predict)
- Underestimating psychology (emotions control decisions)

